### Deployment

- [Heroku Depolyment][heroku]

## Install Rails

- [How to Install Ruby Rails][rails]

## Run Rails Application
#### 1- Pull repository
```sh
$ git clone <repository>
```
#### 2- Open repository folder
```sh
$ cd <dir>
```
#### 3- Run Gem install
```sh
$ bundle install
```
#### 4- Create Databe
```sh
$ bundle exec rake db:migrate
```
#### 5- Seed Database
```sh
$ bundel exec rake db:seed
```
#### 6- Run local Rails web-server
```sh
$ rails s
```

